parameters: Did you sit in a pile of sugar?
Cause you have a pretty sweet ass!
Hey! Do you have an inhaler?
Cause you got that ass, Ma!
Lord Gip is a lucky guy.
Can't you just shut up for a minute?!
I wish your attitude was as pretty as your ass...
You must be Lord Gip's main course...
It'll take hours to eat that big ass of yours!
You must agree to the rules, before I can let you in.
The three rules on the wall!
Rule number one is not to speak until Lord Gip is done talking!
Rule number two is to never touch his pets!
\C[23]Gip doesn't seem like someone to keep pets.
And last but not least, rule number three is to never say the P-word to Lord Gip.
I don't see that rule on the list.
That's because the P-word can't be spoken nor written.
That word starting with the letter P...
No wonder you're such a big lady...
What does he have against the word penis?
I told you to shut up, woman!
If Lord Gip hears you he'll kill us both!
Don't say I didn't warn you.
Now you're allowed to go in...
\C[23]W-What has he done to those poor girls?!
Well... Well... Look who is here...
You're such a shameless woman, Flora...
Your guard did this to me...!
My girls here don't like it when you interrupt me.
Heh... I didn't expect you this soon...
Did you bring me my money?
I came to talk to you about Natalie.
I came to talk to you about Natalie.
That's not the reason why I'm here...
Then why are you wasting my time?!
\C[23]T-Those girls look like they're in pain!
I came here to tell you to stop harassing Natalie!
I didn't think that girl had the guts to tell you about her work.
I was hoping to use that to my advantage...
Oh-ho-ho... You've got me all wrong, Flora.
I would never bother with such petty nonsense.
You would be exactly the person to do just that!
Did you know that this room is soundproof?
W-What does that have to do with anything?
It doesn't matter how loud you scream, no one outside will hear you.
Like I said... I would never scoop that low.
If you touch my family... I'll hurt you.
I said that I'll hurt you if you ever hurt them.
Did you just call me uncle?
You sound exactly like that little pipsqueek!
Promise me that you won't touch them!
You come to my place and tell me what to do?!
But I have to say that I'm impressed, Flora.
You're a woman with courage, which has become a rare sight these days.
I can see why he loved you so much.
He could never stop talking about you.
Hmpf... Well... It has been a pleasure, Flora...
But as you can see, I'm a busy man...
I won't leave until you promise me!
Are you thinking of hurting me?
I've got close to a hundred guards inside this building.
You won't leave this place alive if you touch me.
\C[23]I... I don't think he's bluffing, Dear.
\C[23]We should leave while we can, Dear...
While you're here, why don't you entertain me a little?
Take everything off and dance for me!
I'll\..\..\.. I'll tell everyone about your\..\..\.. secret!
Oh-ho-ho... Empty threats won't work on me.
If you don't stop harassing us...
I will make sure everyone knows about your secret!
Who else did he tell, huh?!
How about that filthy bitch, Scarlett?!
If he wasn't dead already, I would kill him right now!
\C[23]W-What has he done to those poor girls?!
\C[23]He has the whole island in his pockets.
\C[23]But we'll come back to help them...
I told you to get the fuck out of here!
I've never seen him getting that angry before.
I wonder what his secret could be...?
I... I have no idea, but I would like to find out.
He said your father knew about it.
Well... I hope his thugs will stop harassing us now.
I don't know what I would do without you.
Heh... I thought you just said penis...
You finally came to beg for my penis...
\C[23]I think the guard lied to you, Dear...
Do you want it or not?
